1
00:09:39,315 --> 00:09:42,011
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:09:42,084 --> 00:09:45,952
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:09:46,022 --> 00:09:50,015
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:09:50,359 --> 00:09:52,850
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:09:52,929 --> 00:09:56,990
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:09:57,066 --> 00:10:01,025
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:10:02,505 --> 00:10:07,238
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:10:07,944 --> 00:10:10,913
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:10:13,349 --> 00:10:15,442
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:10:16,185 --> 00:10:17,482
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:20,380
<i>Now</i>

12
00:10:28,431 --> 00:10:33,801
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:10:34,003 --> 00:10:35,163
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:10:35,237 --> 00:10:39,037
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:10:39,375 --> 00:10:44,574
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:10:44,847 --> 00:10:46,178
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:10:46,248 --> 00:10:47,647
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:10:47,717 --> 00:10:53,986
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:11:07,852 --> 00:11:09,513
I've... had it...

20
00:11:10,254 --> 00:11:11,551
Oh, Sakura!

21
00:11:12,857 --> 00:11:14,688
For crying out loud,
how far have we walked?

22
00:11:15,292 --> 00:11:17,590
The tower hasn't gotten a bit closer.

23
00:11:18,996 --> 00:11:21,157
Here we can see it
right in front of our eyes.

24
00:11:21,398 --> 00:11:22,660
Strange...

25
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,389
<i>No mistake about it.</i>

26
00:11:24,602 --> 00:11:29,232
It seems that we're already within
the enthusiastic welcome.

27
00:11:30,774 --> 00:11:31,968
Take a look at that.

28
00:11:32,543 --> 00:11:33,373
Huh?

29
00:11:33,878 --> 00:11:35,937
Oh, that can't be!

30
00:11:39,917 --> 00:11:42,044
What on earth is going on?!

31
00:11:42,586 --> 00:11:43,416
No way!

32
00:11:43,954 --> 00:11:44,943
Is it Genjutsu...?

33
00:11:45,523 --> 00:11:49,152
So it seems.
We were lured in perfectly.

34
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:52,656
It appears we were meticulously careful,

35
00:11:53,097 --> 00:11:55,657
and were made to walk
around the same place in a circle.

36
00:11:57,134 --> 00:11:58,533
We're being watched...

37
00:11:59,136 --> 00:12:00,160
Probably.

38
00:12:00,604 --> 00:12:02,629
They intend to wear down
our physical strength and

39
00:12:02,706 --> 00:12:04,901
catch us unprepared when
we're bone tired.

40
00:12:05,409 --> 00:12:07,877
If so, then this follows the enemy strategy.

41
00:12:08,612 --> 00:12:11,547
Then... They'll be coming soon.

42
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:52,017
Humph, they've appeared.

43
00:12:53,090 --> 00:12:55,285
This is the perfect handicap.
Believe it!

44
00:12:55,593 --> 00:13:01,589
<i>Clone vs. Clone.</i>
<i>Mine are Better than Yours!</i>

45
00:13:07,538 --> 00:13:08,869
W-What is this?

46
00:13:10,274 --> 00:13:11,502
It's quite a number.

47
00:13:12,509 --> 00:13:13,999
Moreover, they're clones?

48
00:13:16,413 --> 00:13:18,005
Cornered rats.

49
00:13:21,251 --> 00:13:23,651
Shut up!

50
00:13:30,527 --> 00:13:33,655
<i>Oh, they're quite weak, huh?</i>

51
00:13:34,898 --> 00:13:35,865
Good!

52
00:13:35,933 --> 00:13:37,059
Naruto!

53
00:13:54,885 --> 00:13:57,285
<i>W-What are these guys?</i>

54
00:14:08,699 --> 00:14:10,826
W-What's going on here?

55
00:14:17,775 --> 00:14:19,106
<i>I'll assess this!</i>

56
00:14:19,743 --> 00:14:20,801
Sharingan!

57
00:14:26,817 --> 00:14:27,442
Naruto!

58
00:14:43,834 --> 00:14:44,698
Sasuke!

59
00:14:54,545 --> 00:14:55,569
Sasuke!

60
00:15:01,885 --> 00:15:03,682
<i>W-What's going on?</i>

61
00:15:04,188 --> 00:15:05,120
<i>My body's...</i>

62
00:15:09,793 --> 00:15:10,555
Are you okay?

63
00:15:15,866 --> 00:15:16,662
<i>No mistake.</i>

64
00:15:17,101 --> 00:15:19,262
<i>It's the real thing, not an illusion.</i>

65
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:26,974
- Scroll please.
- Scroll please.

66
00:15:27,578 --> 00:15:32,106
That Kabuto was injured means
these things are actual Shadow Clones?!

67
00:15:33,684 --> 00:15:37,017
B-But... even though Shadow clones
are supposed to vanish

68
00:15:37,087 --> 00:15:40,682
if they take a direct attack,
these things don't vanish.

69
00:15:40,758 --> 00:15:41,884
Does it mean then this is Genjutsu?!

70
00:15:41,959 --> 00:15:43,392
Which is it?!

71
00:15:43,761 --> 00:15:45,456
Scroll please.

72
00:15:45,863 --> 00:15:47,922
Scroll please.

73
00:15:48,332 --> 00:15:50,232
Give me scroll.

74
00:15:51,034 --> 00:15:51,864
Dang it!

75
00:15:52,202 --> 00:15:53,328
It's futile!

76
00:15:53,403 --> 00:15:54,199
Stop!

77
00:15:58,275 --> 00:15:59,742
These things are illusions.

78
00:16:00,410 --> 00:16:01,968
It's an enemy Genjutsu.

79
00:16:03,847 --> 00:16:07,681
B-But, Kabuto's wound is the real thing

80
00:16:08,685 --> 00:16:11,119
No, it's as Sasuke says.

81
00:16:12,122 --> 00:16:15,216
Probably the enemy is hiding somewhere...

82
00:16:15,292 --> 00:16:17,886
and coordinating their attack with
movements of the "Genjutsu Shinobis"

83
00:16:17,961 --> 00:16:20,054
and attacking from a different location.

84
00:16:20,798 --> 00:16:25,360
Pretending as if those
Genjutsu Shinobis are attacking

85
00:16:25,669 --> 00:16:29,833
- Scroll please.
- Scroll please.

86
00:16:34,745 --> 00:16:37,737
Then I'll find the idiot who's behind
the scenes

87
00:16:37,815 --> 00:16:40,215
throwing Kunai knives
and kick his butt, believe it!

88
00:16:40,384 --> 00:16:41,510
Hold it, Naruto.

89
00:16:42,419 --> 00:16:45,582
We've been deceived as
to the source of the Kunai knives...

90
00:16:45,823 --> 00:16:48,018
so we can't discover the precise
location of the enemy like this.

91
00:16:48,492 --> 00:16:49,652
Do you get it?

92
00:16:49,893 --> 00:16:51,793
That is the enemy's purpose.

93
00:16:53,163 --> 00:16:56,599
From a data standpoint, it's a type
who is weak at close combat

94
00:16:56,667 --> 00:16:59,227
and Taijutsu that likes
this kind of attack.

95
00:17:00,103 --> 00:17:04,938
The true enemy won't come out
until we can't move at all.

96
00:17:09,279 --> 00:17:10,507
Listen, everyone!

97
00:17:10,781 --> 00:17:11,941
In any case,

98
00:17:12,015 --> 00:17:14,176
all there is to do now is to fend
off the enemy attack.

99
00:17:17,721 --> 00:17:21,122
Fine, if that's what their plan is...

100
00:17:22,226 --> 00:17:25,286
Now then...
I wonder how far they can hold out.

101
00:17:26,430 --> 00:17:28,057
The night is long.

102
00:17:47,985 --> 00:17:50,215
Man!
This is endless!

103
00:17:51,822 --> 00:17:53,312
Since it's come to this...!

104
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,318
Stop!

105
00:17:54,591 --> 00:17:57,355
Naruto, don't waste your Chakra!

106
00:17:57,694 --> 00:18:00,254
Even if you attack these things,
there's no point!

107
00:18:01,398 --> 00:18:03,958
If I hit them all in
a single sweep,

108
00:18:04,034 --> 00:18:08,164
the enemy won't fire inadvertently
while these things are reverting back.

109
00:18:08,305 --> 00:18:10,569
The hiding place will
be discovered, so.

110
00:18:11,174 --> 00:18:12,732
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

111
00:18:18,782 --> 00:18:19,806
Shadow Clones?!

112
00:18:41,171 --> 00:18:43,196
It's not over yet!

113
00:18:43,540 --> 00:18:45,303
Sasuke, what should we do...?

114
00:18:46,043 --> 00:18:49,638
Man, that loser.
All there is to do is go for it!

115
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,642
B-But...

116
00:18:51,248 --> 00:18:52,078
Indeed...

117
00:18:52,149 --> 00:18:55,380
It's not a situation that
he can get through by himself.

118
00:18:55,786 --> 00:18:56,810
Let's go, Sakura!

119
00:18:56,987 --> 00:18:57,646
Y-Yeah!

120
00:19:23,847 --> 00:19:25,041
I'm not finished yet...

121
00:19:33,357 --> 00:19:34,756
Dawn is breaking

122
00:19:35,525 --> 00:19:37,425
It's finally time for the hunt.

123
00:19:37,894 --> 00:19:39,862
Mubi, that's enough.

124
00:19:41,298 --> 00:19:43,425
We're finished hunting their spirits.

125
00:19:44,501 --> 00:19:47,197
Now what's left is just their bodies.

126
00:19:49,072 --> 00:19:50,232
Lucky.

127
00:19:53,377 --> 00:19:57,905
You're... the one who...
did my left shoulder.

128
00:19:58,915 --> 00:20:00,746
I finally found you.

129
00:20:01,718 --> 00:20:04,084
You really hung me up.

130
00:20:04,388 --> 00:20:05,377
Lucky.

131
00:20:05,689 --> 00:20:07,554
I can finally even the score.

132
00:20:17,536 --> 00:20:21,097
You... really hung me up.

133
00:20:21,573 --> 00:20:22,870
Lucky.

134
00:20:23,308 --> 00:20:25,435
I can finally even the score.

135
00:20:34,219 --> 00:20:34,947
Heh!

136
00:20:37,222 --> 00:20:38,746
Cornered rats.

137
00:20:42,327 --> 00:20:44,192
It went well, Naruto!

138
00:20:55,374 --> 00:20:57,433
W-What the heck
are these guys?!

139
00:20:59,011 --> 00:21:00,308
T-This can't be!

140
00:21:00,379 --> 00:21:01,641
Since when...?!

141
00:21:01,947 --> 00:21:03,107
Idiot!

142
00:21:03,282 --> 00:21:06,251
You finally showed your
true colors, punk!

143
00:21:12,157 --> 00:21:15,684
T-This brat, don't tell me...

144
00:21:16,562 --> 00:21:19,360
The Shadow Clone is just
the preparation for the trick...

145
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:24,801
for me to portray every member
of the team by myself!

146
00:21:26,939 --> 00:21:29,703
At the same time Naruto
lifted the Shadow Clone,

147
00:21:29,775 --> 00:21:32,471
the three of us hid.

148
00:21:34,146 --> 00:21:37,741
The Genjutsu users were
adversely deceived.

149
00:21:44,690 --> 00:21:45,657
Naruto!

150
00:21:47,059 --> 00:21:50,392
Naruto, you've used too much Chakra.

151
00:21:50,862 --> 00:21:52,489
I'll do the rest.

152
00:22:03,809 --> 00:22:08,143
No way! I'm not always going to have
the good parts taken away!

153
00:22:17,289 --> 00:22:20,816
<i>Is this really that Naruto...?</i>

154
00:22:23,028 --> 00:22:26,555
<i>Since when had he improved</i>
<i>this much?</i>

155
00:22:28,767 --> 00:22:30,496
That's some brat...

156
00:22:30,836 --> 00:22:32,531
I can't believe he can still move.

157
00:22:33,839 --> 00:22:35,136
Naruto...

158
00:22:37,643 --> 00:22:39,770
<i>Amazing Chakra stamina...</i>

159
00:22:45,250 --> 00:22:46,945
<i>Right after</i>
<i>a Multiple Shadow Clone Jutsu...</i>

160
00:22:47,019 --> 00:22:50,511
<i>a daring technique that transforms just</i>
<i>three of the bodies into his companions.</i>

161
00:22:50,989 --> 00:22:54,425
<i>To think he can still move</i>
<i>even after doing all that.</i>

162
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:56,887
<i>Here it's the fifth day now.</i>

163
00:22:59,998 --> 00:23:01,158
<i>This kid will transform</i>

164
00:23:01,233 --> 00:23:05,829
<i>if he can just master</i>
<i>the use of his Chakra.</i>

165
00:23:06,672 --> 00:23:08,469
Not bad.

166
00:23:09,107 --> 00:23:13,544
But we're still not unlucky.

167
00:23:16,581 --> 00:23:17,673
There's no time.

168
00:23:19,818 --> 00:23:22,548
This time around,
we'll show you our Ninjutsu!

169
00:23:23,855 --> 00:23:27,120
Ninja Art: Fog, "Clone Jutsu!"

170
00:23:32,864 --> 00:23:33,990
Shadow clones?

171
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:35,858
No, they are plain clones.

172
00:23:36,568 --> 00:23:38,627
However, he's up to something.

173
00:23:38,970 --> 00:23:39,902
Be careful!

174
00:23:40,105 --> 00:23:43,871
Hah! If they are just clones,
then there's one real body.

175
00:23:44,242 --> 00:23:47,507
I'll kick their butts right
and left until I run into him.

176
00:23:47,579 --> 00:23:48,546
You idiot.

177
00:23:48,613 --> 00:23:50,046
Such a tactless thing...

178
00:23:50,615 --> 00:23:51,673
I'm telling you!

179
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:53,684
I'm saying don't stick your nose in!

180
00:23:58,123 --> 00:23:58,953
Naruto!

181
00:23:59,257 --> 00:23:59,985
That's reckless!

182
00:24:00,959 --> 00:24:01,823
Cripes!

183
00:24:09,735 --> 00:24:13,831
<i>From earlier, the nape of my neck</i>
<i>hurts when I use the Sharingan.</i>

184
00:24:14,306 --> 00:24:15,864
<i>Maybe I used too much Chakra.</i>

185
00:24:16,875 --> 00:24:17,705
Dang it!

186
00:24:19,911 --> 00:24:21,344
Dang it. A clone?!

187
00:24:23,048 --> 00:24:23,912
This one, too?!

188
00:24:24,583 --> 00:24:25,379
This one, too?!

189
00:24:26,485 --> 00:24:27,281
This one, too?!

190
00:24:27,953 --> 00:24:29,443
Naruto! Stop!

191
00:24:29,788 --> 00:24:30,948
Are they all fakes?!

192
00:24:31,523 --> 00:24:33,855
Or could it be Genjutsu again?!

193
00:24:34,326 --> 00:24:38,126
This is... the last... Chakra.

194
00:24:40,332 --> 00:24:41,526
Sharingan!

195
00:24:52,377 --> 00:24:53,275
Sasuke!

196
00:24:55,947 --> 00:24:56,879
The bruise again...

197
00:25:00,218 --> 00:25:02,948
Stop using the Sharingan, Sasuke!

198
00:25:05,290 --> 00:25:07,155
It won't do to create an opening!

199
00:25:17,602 --> 00:25:18,626
Kabuto!

200
00:25:23,909 --> 00:25:24,898
Damn it!

201
00:25:25,076 --> 00:25:26,373
Stop! Naruto!

202
00:25:27,846 --> 00:25:29,837
No matter how much
you swing at them,

203
00:25:30,182 --> 00:25:34,676
the real body isn't in those clones.

204
00:25:35,620 --> 00:25:38,145
Then where's the enemy
attacking us from?!

205
00:25:38,557 --> 00:25:42,823
If they are merely clones,
the clones themselves can't attack!

206
00:25:43,261 --> 00:25:45,422
If I knew that, we wouldn't be
having a rough time of it!

207
00:25:45,764 --> 00:25:47,288
This is the enemy's scheme.

208
00:25:49,067 --> 00:25:52,434
<i>Man, I can't use</i>
<i>the Shadow Clone Jutsu anymore...</i>

209
00:25:52,904 --> 00:25:55,236
They've about reached their limit.

210
00:25:55,507 --> 00:25:56,997
Lucky.

211
00:26:07,786 --> 00:26:08,548
<i>That's it!</i>

212
00:26:09,020 --> 00:26:10,681
<i>The real body hides with</i>
<i>the Earth Style Jutsu</i>

213
00:26:10,755 --> 00:26:12,552
<i>and attacks from behind a clone!</i>

214
00:26:16,461 --> 00:26:17,758
Kabuto!

215
00:26:53,098 --> 00:26:56,898
Heh, "it won't do to
create an opening," right?!

216
00:26:57,002 --> 00:27:01,439
Thank you, Naruto.
You saved me.

217
00:27:04,876 --> 00:27:05,934
We're okay here, Naruto!

218
00:27:17,355 --> 00:27:20,085
What happened there? Are you hurt?

219
00:27:20,692 --> 00:27:21,886
That's a terrible bruise.

220
00:27:23,962 --> 00:27:25,259
It's nothing.

221
00:27:29,034 --> 00:27:31,832
Here it is, here it is!

222
00:27:32,003 --> 00:27:34,494
Look, the Heaven scroll!

223
00:27:34,639 --> 00:27:35,765
Good for you.

224
00:27:38,410 --> 00:27:42,346
<i>There's something about this guy...</i>
<i>that I don't like.</i>

225
00:27:53,758 --> 00:27:56,056
Oh, it's you guys.

226
00:27:56,728 --> 00:27:58,252
You're late, Kabuto.

227
00:27:58,730 --> 00:28:00,789
I got a bit involved in something.

228
00:28:01,533 --> 00:28:02,363
Sorry.

229
00:28:02,434 --> 00:28:07,428
But, but...
thanks to you, we got both the scrolls.

230
00:28:07,672 --> 00:28:10,573
No, it's because you guys fought hard.

231
00:28:11,476 --> 00:28:14,070
You were amazing
at the end, Naruto.

232
00:28:18,249 --> 00:28:20,479
We're going through this door.

233
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:23,688
Well then, I wish us both luck.

234
00:28:23,989 --> 00:28:24,819
Yeah!

235
00:28:25,023 --> 00:28:25,921
Yeah!

236
00:28:37,335 --> 00:28:38,563
What of the harvest?

237
00:28:38,636 --> 00:28:39,762
Yes.

238
00:28:39,904 --> 00:28:41,269
More than I expected.

239
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:46,504
I filled in his entire data
from this second exam.

240
00:28:47,312 --> 00:28:48,904
You need this, right?

241
00:28:49,948 --> 00:28:52,849
So, how was it?

242
00:28:54,386 --> 00:28:56,183
Sure enough, it appears you're curious.

243
00:28:56,521 --> 00:28:57,920
Master Orochimaru.

244
00:28:58,890 --> 00:29:01,017
I want to ask your opinion.

245
00:29:01,626 --> 00:29:04,060
As a Sound Village's spy...

246
00:29:04,596 --> 00:29:06,496
That's not necessary, is it?

247
00:29:07,365 --> 00:29:11,358
You will be the one to decide it all, so...

248
00:29:13,338 --> 00:29:17,866
I like that cleverness of yours.

249
00:29:19,711 --> 00:29:20,973
Good work.

250
00:29:22,647 --> 00:29:24,478
There's nobody here.

251
00:29:25,984 --> 00:29:27,815
I'm okay now, Sakura.

252
00:29:28,353 --> 00:29:29,445
O-Okay.

253
00:29:30,321 --> 00:29:32,118
That's too bad!

254
00:29:32,424 --> 00:29:33,914
Cha!

255
00:29:34,059 --> 00:29:37,722
Say say, what're we supposed to do?

256
00:29:37,929 --> 00:29:39,726
Oh! Look at that...

257
00:29:40,231 --> 00:29:45,464
Without... Heaven...
I don't get it at all.

258
00:29:45,603 --> 00:29:46,627
If "Heaven" does not exist,

259
00:29:46,704 --> 00:29:48,171
enrich your knowledge,
and prepare for the chance.

260
00:29:48,473 --> 00:29:49,337
<i>If "Earth" does not exist,</i>

261
00:29:49,407 --> 00:29:51,136
<i>run the fields in search</i>
<i>of an advantage.</i>

262
00:29:51,476 --> 00:29:53,205
<i>Open the series of</i>
<i>Heaven and Earth,</i>

263
00:29:53,278 --> 00:29:55,143
<i>and the perilous way</i>
<i>shall be redressed...</i>

264
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:59,874
<i>This is namely the secret of</i>
<i>"the one that guides..."</i>

265
00:30:00,652 --> 00:30:01,744
What's that?

266
00:30:03,388 --> 00:30:06,721
It looks like there are letters
or something missing there.

267
00:30:07,192 --> 00:30:09,456
It's probably has to do with the scroll.

268
00:30:10,128 --> 00:30:14,462
I think this means we're supposed
to open the Heaven & Earth scroll.

269
00:30:34,385 --> 00:30:36,945
Okay then, I'm going to open it.

270
00:30:39,298 --> 00:30:43,894
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

271
00:30:44,002 --> 00:30:52,102
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

272
00:30:53,178 --> 00:31:01,711
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

273
00:31:02,321 --> 00:31:10,023
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

274
00:31:11,330 --> 00:31:16,962
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

275
00:31:17,035 --> 00:31:20,801
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

276
00:31:20,873 --> 00:31:24,434
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

277
00:31:24,910 --> 00:31:33,318
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

278
00:31:33,719 --> 00:31:38,782
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

279
00:31:38,857 --> 00:31:43,260
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

280
00:31:43,428 --> 00:31:47,091
<i>Just sing.</i>

281
00:31:47,399 --> 00:31:52,496
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

282
00:31:52,638 --> 00:31:54,765
<i>The two are one</i>

283
00:31:54,873 --> 00:32:01,142
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

284
00:32:01,747 --> 00:32:06,741
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

285
00:32:11,267 --> 00:32:12,291
What's this, what's this?

286
00:32:12,435 --> 00:32:14,869
Here I thought that the really
strong ones were remaining

287
00:32:14,938 --> 00:32:18,499
but Hinata, Kiba, Shikamaru,
all of the Leaf Village rookies are here.

288
00:32:18,608 --> 00:32:20,576
And that Lee's team, too.

289
00:32:20,643 --> 00:32:23,168
So much for getting all inflated.

290
00:32:23,346 --> 00:32:26,179
Well, I'm the man who's going
to become the Hokage.

291
00:32:26,249 --> 00:32:28,183
I must impress them and

292
00:32:28,251 --> 00:32:31,914
show that I'm not in the same class
as any ordinary blockhead!

293
00:32:32,188 --> 00:32:36,682
Next episode: "Surviving the Cut!
The Rookie Nine Together Again!
